  EffectDiscription_ENG: "[Digivolve][Dorugoramon]: Cost 2 \n\n[Trash] [All Turns]
    When one of your [Dorugoramon] would be deleted, by digivolving it into this
    card without paying the cost, prevent that deletion.\n[When Digivolving] \uFF1CDe-Digivolve3\uFF1E
    1 of your opponent's Digimon (Trash up to 3 cards from the top. You can't trash
    past level 3 cards). Then, if [Dorugoramon] is in this Digimon's digivolution
    cards or this card is digivolving from the trash, delete all of your opponent's
    Digimon with the lowest level.\n[All Turns] [Once Per Turn] When another Digimon
    is deleted, you may unsuspend this Digimon."
